Surface:   Led by Guy Hands , managing director for Nomura International 's Principal Finance Group , the unit has completed more than $ 11 billion in securitizations since 1995 , including the 944 million pound securitization of Angel Trains , which the U.K. government sold as part of its rail privatization program ; the 904 million pound securitization of Annington Homes , a group of 57,000 British military houses ; and the 249 million pound securitization of the Phoenix Inns pub chain Nomura also bought from GrandMet and Fosters .

Annotation:  Led by Guy Hands , managing director for Nomura International 's Principal Finance Group , the unit has completed more than $ 11 billion in securitizations since 1995 , including the 944 million pound securitization of Angel Trains , which the U.K. government sold as part of its rail privatization program ; the 904 million pound securitization of Annington Homes , a group of 57,000 British military houses ; and the 249 million pound securitization of the Phoenix Inns pub chain Nomura also bought from GrandMet and Fosters .
